{"tid":261112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛蛙好大隻","createTime":"2017-05-28T07:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T04:21:11.000Z","uid":72009,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e334ddeff47d8e1267fda08dc2f13a2e2e15b7b","tid":261112,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"美國男子藍傑爾（Markcuz&nbsp; Rangel）在打獵時獵殺一隻重近6公斤的巨型牛蛙（bull frog），他一手拿槍，一手抓著牛蛙屍體拍照，他將照片與狩獵團體分享，上傳臉書，照片中的「怪獸牛蛙」身長似乎有小孩那麼高，看起來十分駭人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》前天報導，照片引發網友熱議，有人認為不是真的，「放大就看到不是真的」，也有人說：「這是怪物，不是蛙。」不過德州公園與野生動物部官員證實相片是真，但「牠不如看起來那麼巨大。這是錯覺，將牛蛙舉近鏡頭，令牠看來拉長了，就像漁夫拿著魚舉起，讓牠看來更大一樣。當然這仍是一隻大牛蛙」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170528/640_dac0328efec51e70eb8263f54c80935e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170528%2F640_dac0328efec51e70eb8263f54c80935e.jpg&h=fb92e67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29f6fd3cafc249ed5ad295e48f7fbfdea0ec113","tid":261112,"uid":114097,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"夏.....夏美大人"},{"pid":"6bc8fa3f2f65116ed5997ef4e883e8036a85f192","tid":261112,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"Kerokerokerokerokerokerokerokero"},{"pid":"4896141f168d3e927fb8ad37a15a8ff3ff057f22","tid":261112,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"好肉酸呀隻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6ac18a44063be744fa3bed55aa7086947b6f6a","tid":261112,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國男子藍傑爾（Markcuz&amp;nbsp; Rangel）在打獵時獵殺一隻重近6公斤的巨型牛蛙（bull frog），他一手拿槍，一手抓著牛蛙屍體拍照，他將照片與狩獵團體分享，上傳臉書，照片中的「怪獸牛蛙」身長似乎有小孩那麼高，看起來十分駭人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》前天報導，照片引發網友熱議，有人認為不是真的